Local steps for install and build
* configure the build using `meson configure build`
* run the build using `ninja -C build install`
* if dependency is missing, install dependency and rerun the build
* run the application using `build/src/atomix`

Local flatpak steps for install and build
* build the flatpak using `flatpak-builder --install --user atomix org.gnome.Atomix.Devel.json --force-clean`
* run the flatpak application using `flatpak run org.gnome.Atomix`
